          </h1>
          <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-muted-foreground sm:text-xl lg:mx-0">
            Executives get the roadmap, engineers get typed code, creators get polished experiences—all generated from one English description. No backlog bottlenecks. No translation taxes. ONE turns intent into deployed software in minutes.
          </p>
