                Get production-grade TypeScript you can merge today.
              </CardDescription>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent className="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <p>Convex actions, Effect workflows, tests, and infrastructure scaffolding come pre-validated.</p>
              <p>Ontology contracts mean no ambiguous requirements, edge cases, or handoff meetings.</p>
              <p>CI-ready output with linting, typing, and docs so teams focus on differentiation.</p>
