            <div class="rounded-lg border border-border/50 bg-background p-6">
              <pre class="overflow-x-auto text-sm leading-relaxed"><code>{`FEATURE: Let fans buy creator tokens

INPUT:
  - fan: who is buying
  - token: which creator's token
  - amount: how many tokens
  - usd amount: price in dollars

FLOW:

CHECK fan exists
CHECK token exists
CHECK amount > 0

DO TOGETHER:
  - CALL Stripe to charge payment
  - CALL Blockchain to mint tokens

IF ANY FAIL:
  - CALL Stripe to refund
  - CALL Blockchain to burn tokens

RECORD tokens purchased
UPDATE fan's balance
GIVE confirmation`}</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
